import React from 'react'
import {Link, withRouter } from "react-router-dom";
import { Button } from './styles/header'

const Header = () => (
  <>
    <Link to="/">
      <Button>
        HOME
      </Button>
    </Link>
    <Link to="/login">
      <Button>
        LOGIN
      </Button>
    </Link>
    <Link to="/help">
      <Button>
        HELP-CENTER
      </Button>
    </Link>
    <Link to="/about-us">
      <Button>
        ABOUT US
      </Button>
    </Link>
  </>
)

export default withRouter(Header);
